\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {10}{\ignorespaces 在采用AdaIN的\texttt  {up\_blocks.0.attentions.1}内5个self-attention processor配置（本文方法）下不同$\gamma $值的风格迁移效果。从左至右$\gamma =0.2,0.4,0.8,1.0$，可清晰观察风格纹理随$\gamma $增大而逐步增强的渐变过程。}}{7}{figure.caption.15}\protected@file@percent }
